{"tid":2500921,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"專登返去問人本書叫咩名會唔會好尷尬？","createTime":"2021-04-23T04:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T09:41:52.000Z","uid":137043,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e16bf27bd577f471da8e6acffe3cf0f29e1117df","tid":2500921,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"[朋友借ac]<br />\n之前去一間舖頭買嘢<br />\n有個店員可能見無咩客就過嚟吹水<br />\n吹吹下佢介紹咗幾本書叫我睇<br />\n轉個頭我就唔記得書名<br />\n如果因為幾本書專登返去搵店員問會唔會好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我對嗰幾本書真係有啲興趣<br />\n應該點問好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果到時佢有同事喺隔離點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ca2099dfa86329e048a83259a0214cdd6b12d6","tid":2500921,"uid":220431,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"唔問蝕底個個係你自己"},{"pid":"fc78a7d6f0052e2ccee8377d455de033c6baaf41","tid":2500921,"uid":312768,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:37:12.000Z","msg":"咁都尷尬唔好出街算啦 你驚佢已經唔記得個書名好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非你見人靚女想借d意拎contact 咁就要提下你照照鏡先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24adc430340113f99f769adc34454a1bf63f5228","tid":2500921,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17ca2099dfa86329e048a83259a0214cdd6b12d6","tid":2500921,"uid":220431,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"唔問蝕底個個係你自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"如果去到佢唔喺度點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間舖唔係for得閒無聊入去行嗰種<br />\n一入去其他店員一定會notice到<br />\n就係怕嗰種尷尬<br />\n望一望唔喺度就走？"},{"pid":"10a241d2269ae4b9158507021e6460fa783c4b08","tid":2500921,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04